{"TopicId":128173,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"Is there a way to install your own flags","CreatedByName":"Brigadier","CreatedById":147109,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T06:58:32Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Brigadier","CreatedById":147109,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T06:58:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve tried searching the forums but the search engine keeps returning an EX2 error with no descriptive text so if this has been asked and answered before, my apologies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any way to add your own flag to the game?\u00A0 By \u0027flag\u0027 I mean the default mission flag that you select at the beginning of a new game.\u00A0 I\u0027ve searched the KSP directory for any clues but can\u0027t find anything obvious.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-19T06:59:13Z\u0022 title=\u002212/19/2015 06:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 19, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Brigadier\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T07:22:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll you need to do is put an appropriately sized file in the \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027courier new\u0027, courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Egamedata\\Squad\\flags\u003C/span\u003E directory. Look at the flags there to see the correct sizes. I think as long as you keep the multiples correct, any actual size will do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think also that any directory anywhere off of \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027courier new\u0027, courier, monospace;\u0022\u003EGamedata\u003C/span\u003E named \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027courier new\u0027, courier, monospace;\u0022\u003EFlags\u003C/span\u003E will load the images within as flags. At least, I have my flag in \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027courier new\u0027, courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Egamedata\\00_mine\\Flags\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-19T17:45:50Z\u0022 title=\u002212/19/2015 05:45  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 19, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by 5thHorseman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T07:27:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSure is! Check out the \u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Tutorial:Create_custom_flags!\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ecustom flag tutorial\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0on the wiki for full details.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Brigadier","CreatedById":147109,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-19T19:40:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57865-stibbons/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F128173-is-there-a-way-to-install-your-own-flags%252F\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57865-stibbons/\u0022 title=\u0022Go to stibbons\u0027s profile\u0022\u003Estibbons,\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-5thhorseman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F128173-is-there-a-way-to-install-your-own-flags%252F\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-5thhorseman/\u0022 title=\u0022Go to 5thHorseman\u0027s profile\u0022\u003E5thHorseman\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMany thanks...I was obviously looking in the wrong place.\u00A0 I never thought to look in the wiki.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-19T19:43:23Z\u0022 title=\u002212/19/2015 07:43  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 19, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Brigadier\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}